---
// 核心产品介绍组件
---

<section id="products" class="products-section py-5xl">
  <div class="container">
    
    <!-- 标题区域 -->
    <div class="section-header text-center mb-5xl">
      <h2 class="section-title chinese-text font-bold mb-md">
        核心产品
      </h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle chinese-text opacity-80 mb-xl">
        端到端确定性物流解决方案
      </p>
      <p class="section-description english-text small-element opacity-70">
        Comprehensive end-to-end logistics solutions with measurable certainty
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 产品网格 -->
    <div class="products-grid">
      
      <!-- 库雷克绿通 -->
      <div class="product-hero card mb-5xl">
        <div class="product-content grid grid-2 gap-5xl items-center">
          <div class="product-info">
            <div class="product-badge chinese-text mb-lg">
              <span class="badge-icon">🌊</span>
              <span class="badge-text">跨里海中间走廊</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="product-title chinese-text font-bold mb-lg">
              库雷克绿通
              <span class="english-text font-normal opacity-70">Caspian Middle Corridor</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="product-description chinese-text mb-xl">
              跨里海中间走廊关键节点的优先通行方案，服务中国—中亚—南高加索—土耳其—欧洲的多向货流。
              港口协同排期、舱位协调、报关报检、港内作业、跨段接驳、异常处置预案。
            </p>
            
            <div class="product-features mb-xl">
              <div class="feature-item mb-md">
                <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
                <div class="feature-content">
                  <h4 class="chinese-text font-medium">优先通行</h4>
                  <p class="chinese-text small-element opacity-80">港口协同排期，舱位协调保障</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-item mb-md">
                <div class="feature-icon">📋</div>
                <div class="feature-content">
                  <h4 class="chinese-text font-medium">一站式清关</h4>
                  <p class="chinese-text small-element opacity-80">报关报检，港内作业统筹</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-item">
                <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
                <div class="feature-content">
                  <h4 class="chinese-text font-medium">全程可视</h4>
                  <p class="chinese-text small-element opacity-80">节点里程碑，异常T+0预警</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="product-sla">
              <div class="sla-grid grid grid-3 gap-md">
                <div class="sla-item text-center">
                  <div class="sla-value accent-number font-black">标准</div>
                  <div class="sla-label chinese-text small-element">15-18天</div>
                </div>
                <div class="sla-item text-center">
                  <div class="sla-value accent-number font-black">加急</div>
                  <div class="sla-label chinese-text small-element">12-15天</div>
                </div>
                <div class="sla-item text-center">
                  <div class="sla-value accent-number font-black">绿通</div>
                  <div class="sla-label chinese-text small-element">10-12天</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="product-visual">
            <div class="route-map">
              <div class="route-line"></div>
              <div class="route-points">
                <div class="point point-start">
                  <div class="point-dot"></div>
                  <div class="point-label chinese-text">中国</div>
                </div>
                <div class="point point-mid">
                  <div class="point-dot"></div>
                  <div class="point-label chinese-text">库雷克港</div>
                </div>
                <div class="point point-end">
                  <div class="point-dot"></div>
                  <div class="point-label chinese-text">欧洲</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="route-info">
                <div class="info-item">
                  <span class="chinese-text font-medium">覆盖路径：</span>
                  <span class="chinese-text small-element">中国-哈萨克斯坦-阿塞拜疆-格鲁吉亚-土耳其-欧洲</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 其他核心产品 -->
      <div class="products-list grid grid-2 gap-xl">
        
        <!-- 清关与合规 -->
        <div class="product-card card">
          <div class="product-header mb-lg">
            <div class="product-icon">📝</div>
            <div class="product-meta">
              <h3 class="product-name chinese-text font-bold">清关与合规</h3>
              <p class="english-text small-element opacity-70">Kazakhstan & EAEU Customs</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="product-desc chinese-text mb-lg opacity-90">
            进口报关、税则归类、原产地与合规证明、EAEU技术法规（TR CU）与本地标准衔接。
            一次性合规设计 > 事后补救。
          </p>
          
          <div class="product-tags">
            <span class="tag chinese-text">进口报关</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">税则归类</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">EAEU法规</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">原产地证明</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 仓储与分拨 -->
        <div class="product-card card">
          <div class="product-header mb-lg">
            <div class="product-icon">🏭</div>
            <div class="product-meta">
              <h3 class="product-name chinese-text font-bold">仓储与分拨</h3>
              <p class="english-text small-element opacity-70">Warehousing & Distribution</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="product-desc chinese-text mb-lg opacity-90">
            保税/普通/温控仓；增值服务（贴标、分拣、轻加工、套件化）。
            WMS/OMS对接，SKU级可视化，盘点与损益报告。
          </p>
          
          <div class="product-tags">
            <span class="tag chinese-text">保税仓储</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">温控管理</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">增值服务</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">系统对接</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 干线联运 -->
        <div class="product-card card">
          <div class="product-header mb-lg">
            <div class="product-icon">🚛</div>
            <div class="product-meta">
              <h3 class="product-name chinese-text font-bold">干线联运</h3>
              <p class="english-text small-element opacity-70">Multimodal Transport</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="product-desc chinese-text mb-lg opacity-90">
            海运与里海联运、中亚/外高加索铁路、跨境公路（含TIR）、阿克套与阿拉木图空运。
            多式联运资源统筹，节点可控。
          </p>
          
          <div class="product-tags">
            <span class="tag chinese-text">海运联运</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">铁路运输</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">TIR公路</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">航空货运</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 最后一公里 -->
        <div class="product-card card">
          <div class="product-header mb-lg">
            <div class="product-icon">📦</div>
            <div class="product-meta">
              <h3 class="product-name chinese-text font-bold">最后一公里</h3>
              <p class="english-text small-element opacity-70">Last Mile Delivery</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="product-desc chinese-text mb-lg opacity-90">
            B2B配送：门店、经销与项目工地直达；电商/快件：时段投递、逆向揽收。
            配送准时达率、签收完整性、客户NPS跟踪。
          </p>
          
          <div class="product-tags">
            <span class="tag chinese-text">B2B配送</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">电商快递</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">预约投递</span>
            <span class="tag chinese-text">逆向物流</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
      
      <!-- 金融增值服务 -->
      <div class="financial-services mt-5xl">
        <div class="service-header text-center mb-3xl">
          <h3 class="chinese-text font-bold text-2xl mb-md">金融增值服务</h3>
          <p class="english-text small-element opacity-70">Financial Value-Added Services</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="financial-grid grid grid-3 gap-lg">
          <div class="financial-item text-center">
            <div class="financial-icon mb-md">🛡️</div>
            <h4 class="chinese-text font-bold mb-sm">保险保障</h4>
            <p class="chinese-text small-element opacity-80">货运险、责任险全覆盖</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="financial-item text-center">
            <div class="financial-icon mb-md">💱</div>
            <h4 class="chinese-text font-bold mb-sm">结算换汇</h4>
            <p class="chinese-text small-element opacity-80">多币种结算与汇率优化</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="financial-item text-center">
            <div class="financial-icon mb-md">💰</div>
            <h4 class="chinese-text font-bold mb-sm">资金流优化</h4>
            <p class="chinese-text small-element opacity-80">账期管理与现金周转提升</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    
    <!-- 立即行动 -->
    <div class="action-section text-center mt-5xl">
      <div class="action-content">
        <h3 class="chinese-text font-bold text-2xl mb-lg">开始您的确定性物流之旅</h3>
        <p class="chinese-text mb-2xl opacity-80">
          让我们用系统化的确定性，为您创造长期价值
        </p>
        
        <div class="action-buttons flex justify-center gap-lg flex-wrap">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary chinese-text">
            获取绿通名额
            <span class="english-text small-element">Get Green Channel Access</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/solutions" class="btn btn-outline chinese-text">
            查看解决方案
            <span class="english-text small-element">View Solutions</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .products-section {
    background: 
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.02) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 70%, rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  /* 库雷克绿通主打产品 */
  .product-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.05) 0%, rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.02) 100%);
    border: 2px solid rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
    padding: var(--space-16);
  }
  
  .product-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    background: rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  
  .product-title {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  
  .product-description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  
  /* 产品特性 */
  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .feature-icon {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .feature-content h4 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  /* SLA展示 */
  .product-sla {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .sla-value {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  
  .sla-label {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }
  
  /* 路线可视化 */
  .route-map {
    position: relative;
    height: 300px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.05) 0%, transparent 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: var(--space-12);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .route-line {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 10%;
    right: 10%;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-accent) 0%, rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.3) 100%);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }
  
  .route-points {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100px;
  }
  
  .point {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .point-dot {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border: 3px solid var(--bg-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--color-accent);
  }
  
  .point-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }
  
  .route-info {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  /* 产品卡片 */
  .product-card {
    padding: var(--space-12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .product-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
  }
  
  .product-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .product-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .product-name {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  .product-desc {
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  /* 标签 */
  .product-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }
  
  .tag {
    background: rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3);
    border-radius: 16px;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  /* 金融服务 */
  .financial-services {
    background: rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.03);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: var(--space-16) var(--space-12);
  }
  
  .financial-icon {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
  }
  
  .financial-item h4 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  
  /* 行动区域 */
  .action-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.05) 0%, rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.02) 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: var(--space-16) var(--space-12);
  }
  
  .action-buttons .btn {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-12);
    min-width: 200px;
  }
  
  /* 响应式设计 */
  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .product-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-16);
    }
    
    .product-visual {
      order: -1;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .products-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }
    
    .sla-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-3);
    }
    
    .financial-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }
    
    .action-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }
    
    .action-buttons .btn {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 280px;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .product-hero {
      padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-6);
    }
    
    .route-map {
      height: 200px;
      padding: var(--space-6);
    }
    
    .point-label {
      font-size: var(--text-xs);
    }
  }
</style>